originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name, 
    t.title AS movie_title, 
    c.kind AS cast_type, 
    p.info AS person_info,
    k.keyword AS movie_keyword 
FROM 
    aka_name a 
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id 
JOIN 
    title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id 
JOIN 
    comp_cast_type c ON ci.person_role_id = c.id 
JOIN 
    person_info p ON a.person_id = p.person_id 
JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id 
JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id 
WHERE 
    t.production_year > 2000 
    AND c.kind LIKE 'Actor%'
    AND p.info_type_id IN (SELECT id FROM info_type WHERE info = 'Biography') 
ORDER BY 
    a.name, t.production_year DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."ACTOR_NAME", "t5"."ACTOR_NAME") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t5"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t5"."CAST_TYPE", "t5"."PERSON_INFO", "t5"."MOVIE_KEYWORD", "t5"."production_year"
FROM (SELECT "aka_name"."name" AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t3"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "t2"."kind" AS "CAST_TYPE", "person_info"."info" AS "PERSON_INFO", "keyword"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "t3"."production_year"
FROM "keyword"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "id" AS "ID"
FROM "info_type"
WHERE "info" = 'Biography') AS "t1" INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "person_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "person_info"."person_id") ON "t1"."ID" = "person_info"."info_type_id" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "s1"
WHERE "kind" LIKE 'Actor%') AS "t2" INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "t2"."id" = "cast_info"."person_role_id" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "title"
WHERE "production_year" > 2000) AS "t3" INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "t3"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id") ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "t3"."id") ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id") ON "keyword"."id" = "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
ORDER BY "aka_name"."name", "t3"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t5"
